library(readr)
getwd()
## [1] "/Users/erik/Documents/blog/data"
suppressMessages(Shakespeare <- read_csv("Shakespeare.csv"))
library(treemap)
treemap(Shakespeare,
        index=(c("Play_ID")),
        vSize="nLines")

library(dplyr)
Shakespeare %>% 
  group_by(Play_ID) %>% 
  summarise(s = sum(nLines)) %>% 
  arrange(desc(s))

library(sunburstR)
str2 = Shakespeare %>% 
  mutate(str = paste0("Type:",Type,"-","Play:",Play_ID,"-","Character:",Character_ID)) %>% 
  select(str, nLines)
sunburst(str2)
